{"tid":1726201,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇諗過股市先係春袋","createTime":"2019-11-16T05:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T08:13:00.000Z","uid":260275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9b5f6c2bb27fd6b9115281bcea82e82fefd2fb53","tid":1726201,"uid":260275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:00:37.000Z","msg":"搞咗成個禮拜被罷工都好似冇乜點影響個市<br />\n係就係跌咗幾百點<br />\n有冇諗過點樣可以跌得多啲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 金融業扮工</span><br />\n見到好多中環金融佬出黎和你lunch贖罪<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但你lunch前已經開咗市</span><br />\n已經做咗好多野<br />\n扮工令行政野做慢咗先可以慢慢咁控制個交易市場？<br />\n始終唔係金融佬唔識咁多<br />\n但我淨係知如果你罷唔到就要<span style=\"font-size: large;\">扮工</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 組織金融業公會</span><br />\n我見大三罷好似有人整緊啲公會出黎<br />\n但係可唔可以優先搞咗金融業先<br />\n因為佢真係春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過依家最緊要係做好地區文宣 解釋翻呢幾日嘅事同TVB冇報嘅事先<br />\n拉中間派嘅票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f3a5e286db43e9eadfd08fdedeeb0941759777","tid":1726201,"uid":260275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:01:53.000Z","msg":"p牌自推"},{"pid":"467284f267d956e0c7bc6958936cc031fb83f7d4","tid":1726201,"uid":260275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:02:03.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"1fa9263cde3fe34194fbdf91a18b8c32ca829ea2","tid":1726201,"uid":260275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:02:14.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"5133ddd2995bfa7599b5e752ff19bf184058e904","tid":1726201,"uid":260275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:02:24.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"cbef480a97b9a5ed5be4ad883232a1cc957e2fe4","tid":1726201,"uid":260275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:02:36.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"691493bf4130ff0fe1b21d017070e3f56235c